  "title": "Class 3 Driver (Central - 6 days)",
  "description": "<h3>Job Vacancy: Class 3 Driver</h3><h3>Industry: Wholesale & Logistics <br />Work Location: Tiong Bahru</h3><p>⸻</p><h3>Salary</h3><p>SGD 2,400 – SGD 2,800</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Working Hours</h3><p>Working Schedule: Shift Basis (To Be Confirmed)</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Monthly Rest Days</h3><p>4 days</p><p>⸻</p><h3>About the Company</h3><p><u>A rice wholesale firm in Singapore providing distribution and delivery services to customers across various locations.</u></p><p>⸻</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p></p><p>Perform delivery of rice products according to assigned routes and schedules<br /></p><p>Ensure safe driving and proper handling of goods during loading and unloading<br /></p><p>Assist with lifting and moving rice sacks during busy periods<br /></p><p>Maintain cleanliness and basic checks of the assigned delivery vehicle<br /></p><p>Follow company procedures and delivery documentation requirements</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Job Requirements</h3><p>Prior experience in delivery driving and route familiarity is preferred<br /></p><p>Physically able to handle and move goods as required for deliveries<br /></p><p>Responsible, punctual, and safety-conscious while on the road<br /></p><p>Good communication skills</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Benefits</h3><p>Employment terms and benefits in accordance with Ministry of Manpower (MOM) regulations</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Contract</h3><p>Not specified</p><p>⸻</p><h3>Interview Method</h3><p>Video interview or On-site interview</p>",
